{"tid":2211573,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone Xs 叉電位問題","createTime":"2020-09-21T08:14:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T10:42:53.000Z","uid":167573,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7a6c850b11b5571449d34a1d90c3e715b2426277","tid":2211573,"uid":167573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:14:50.000Z","msg":"其實呢個問題都煩咗我差唔多兩年.<br />\n大家部iPhone有無試過叉叉下電個陣部電話郁一郁就會斷電?<br />\n<br />\n點為之郁呢, <br />\n就係你拎起放低部電話個陣 <br />\n或者<br />\n你部電話拎起部電話諗住打橫睇片個陣.<br />\n<br />\n我本身都用緊原裝條lighting線.<br />\n我開頭都以為係自己條iPhone線有問題.<br />\n之後買咗momax 條usb c to lighting 線 都係咁.<br />\n後尾再買埋momax 條編織2米usb c to lighting 線 都係解決唔到問題<br />\n<br />\n我部xs一買返嚟個陣用咗兩三個星期已經開始係咁.<br />\n用咗兩個幾月已經拎過返apple 換過.<br />\n之後上年11月又換過. <br />\n即係3部 iPhone xs 都係咁.<br />\n其實apple store d staff 話你有apple care, 咁咪換到無事為止<br />\n不過每次換電話都搞成大半日, 所以我都費事成日去換<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://discussions.apple.com/thread/8594741\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscussions.apple.com%2Fthread%2F8594741&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZojk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=f82790bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://discussions.apple.com/thread/8594741</a><br />\n個情況就好似呢篇嘢講咁.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kX_mVeBtdrc&amp;t=28s&amp;ab_channel=HelpfulDIY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkX_mVeBtdrc%26t%3D28s%26ab_channel%3DHelpfulDIY&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZojk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=23be674f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kX_mVeBtdrc&amp;t=28s&amp;ab_channel=HelpfulDIY</a><br />\n或者好似呢條片咁<br />\n<br />\n其實主要都係話 可能個頭有d污糟嘢係入面 叫你清潔下佢<br />\n但無理由我新機用幾個星期咁快就污糟.<br />\n<br />\n我已經好耐未試過成功叉一次電而個電話係唔會斷電....<br />\n有無巴打情況又係咁???"},{"pid":"357d09520b54c509e2d4f6ba5058dd4d31c494f9","tid":2211573,"uid":340623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:21:11.000Z","msg":"試過要頂一頂（上下方向，唔係出入方向）先叉到"},{"pid":"641f8aac2c3ca8f64bfbf6c30793f6bee9217268","tid":2211573,"uid":167573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"357d09520b54c509e2d4f6ba5058dd4d31c494f9","tid":2211573,"uid":340623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:21:11.000Z","msg":"試過要頂一頂（上下方向，唔係出入方向）先叉到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:22:08.000Z","msg":"但我每次一郁就又再斷電"},{"pid":"ef17b17ce1661c88883e7f89f78d92acfef9f372","tid":2211573,"uid":261332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:23:51.000Z","msg":"最後發現原來係你個火牛問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98df785c462cc140c1f2bc226d227b934e70fab8","tid":2211573,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:25:04.000Z","msg":"先檢查一下差電位有冇塵，因為經常積塵。<br />\n如果有嘅話，用支針了乾淨個叉電位先。<br />\n再試下換一條靚啲嘅叉電線，比如first champion"},{"pid":"e1139d6d6e68901e4a8f0f337061ce49a3edde54","tid":2211573,"uid":25619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:25:41.000Z","msg":"撩乾淨再試下<br />\n我之前撩咗好多塵出黎就次次都叉得好穩定"},{"pid":"8157f004b7c64814bc0c282a331b340730f2c9d0","tid":2211573,"uid":161988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:25:51.000Z","msg":"Same"},{"pid":"d8ef7043a71498b59cc356556b32fc44869046a2","tid":2211573,"uid":167573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef17b17ce1661c88883e7f89f78d92acfef9f372","tid":2211573,"uid":261332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:23:51.000Z","msg":"最後發現原來係你個火牛問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:28:50.000Z","msg":"應該唔係火牛有事<br />\n因為用尿袋都有呢個情況發生."},{"pid":"b36962d57600c7992f7c4551f507802cc466b37a","tid":2211573,"uid":167573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98df785c462cc140c1f2bc226d227b934e70fab8","tid":2211573,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:25:04.000Z","msg":"先檢查一下差電位有冇塵，因為經常積塵。<br />\n如果有嘅話，用支針了乾淨個叉電位先。<br />\n再試下換一條靚啲嘅叉電線，比如first champion"},"cited